div1.p: In the Circuit Court of the United States Ninth Circuit
Applicants in support of Petition for Writ of Habeas Corpus
FILED IN THE U.S. CIRCUIT COURT, DIST. OF WASHINGTON. OCT 7 1904 A. REEVES. AYRES, Clerk A.N. Moore Dep.
United States District Court for the District of Washington. In re Ham Hung Wah
To the Clerk of the above Entitled Court: You will please enter my appearance as Attorney for petitioner in the above entitled cause
NOTICE.-Attorneys will please endorse their own Filings. Rule 47.
United States Circuits Court District of Washington.
In re Ham Hung Wah, On Habeas Corpus
Filed Oct 8 1904 A. Reeves Ayres, Clerk By Deputy Clerk
